quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  15,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  15,1,a l- ray yeh ayaat hain kitaab Ellahi aur quran Mubin kihalal hi behtar aur paindah tar hai
  15,2,baeed nahi ke aik waqt woh aa jaye jab wohi log jinhon ne aaj ( dawat islam ko qubool karne se ) inkaar kar diya hai pachta pachta kar kahin ge ke kash hum ne sir tasleem khham kar diya hota
  15,3,"chhorro inhain khayen, pi-yen , mazay karen, aur behlawaymein daaley rakhay inn ko jhooti umeed anqareeb aِnhin maloom ho jaye ga"
  15,4,hum ne iss se pehlay jis bastii ko bhi halaak kya hai is ke liye aik khaas mohlat amal likhi ja chuki thi
  15,5,"koi qoum nah apne waqt muqarrar se pehlay halaak hosakti hai, nah uss ke baad chhuut sakti hai"
  15,6,"yeh log kehte hain"" ae woh shakhs jis par zikar nazil howa hai, to yaqeenan deewana hai"
  15,7,"agar to sacha hai to hamaray samnay firshton ko le kyun nahi aata? """
  15,8,"hum firshton ko yun hi nahi utaar diya karte woh jab utartay hain to haq ke sath utartay hain, aur phir logon ko mohlat nahi di jati"
  15,9,"raha yeh zikar, to iss ko hum ne nazil kya hai aur hum khud iss ke nigehbaan hain"
  15,10,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum tum se pehlay bohat si guzri hui qomon mein rasool bhaij chuke hain"
  15,11,kabhi aisa nahi howa ke unn ke paas koi rasool aaya ho aur onhon ne uss ka mazaq nah uraya ho
  15,12,mujrimeen ke dilon mein to hum is zikar ko isi terhan ( salakh ke manind ) guzartay hain
  15,13,woh iss par imaan nahi laya karte qadeem se iss qamash ke logon ka yahi tareeqa chala aa raha hai
  15,14,agar hum unn par aasman ka koi darwaaza khol dete aur woh din d_harhe uss mein charhne bhi lagtay
  15,15,"tab bhi woh yahi kehte ke hamari aankhon ko dhoka ho raha hai, balkay hum par jaadoo kar diya gaya hai"
  15,16,"yeh hamari car farmai hai ke aasman mein hum ne bohat se mazboot qilay banaye, unn ko dekhnay walon ke liye muzayyan kya"
  15,17,aur har shetan mardood se un ko mehfooz kar diya
  15,18,"koi shetan un mein raah nahi pa sakta, ila yeh ke kuch sun gun le le aur jab woh sun gun lainay ki koshish karta hai to aik shola roshan uss ka peecha karta hai"
  15,19,"hum ne zameen ko phelaya, uss mein pahar jamaye, is mein har noo ki nabataat theek theek napi tali miqdaar ke sath ugai"
  15,20,"aur is mein maeeshat ke asbaab faraham kiye, tumahray liye bhi aur unn bohat si makhloqaat ke liye bhi jin ke Razaq tum nahi ho"
  15,21,"koi cheez aisi nahi jis ke khazanay hamaray paas nah hon, aur jis cheez ko bhi hum nazil karte hain aik muqarrar miqdaar mein nazil karte hain"
  15,22,"baar aawar hawaon ko hum hi bhaijtay hain, phir aasman se pani barastee hain, aur uss pani se tumhe sairaab karte hain iss doulat ke khazana daar tum nahi ho"
  15,23,"zindagi aur mout hum dete hain, aur hum hi sab ke waris honay walay hain"
  15,24,"pehlay jo log tum mein se ho guzray hain unn ko bhi hum ne dekh rakha hai, aur baad ke anay walay bhi hamari nigah mein hain"
  15,25,"yaqeenan tumhara rab un sab ko akhatta kere ga, woh hakeem bhi hai aur Aleem bhi"
  15,26,hum ne ensaan ko stri hui matti ke sokhey gaaray se banaya
  15,27,aur uss se pehlay junoo ko hum aag ki lapat se peda kar chuke thay
  15,28,"phir yaad karo uss mauqa ko jab tumahray rab ne firshton se kaha ke"" mein sari hui matti ke sokhey gaaray se aik bashar peda kar raha hon"
  15,29,"jab mein ussay poora bana chukun aur is mein apni rooh se kuch phoonk dun to tum sab is ke agay sjday mein gir jana """
  15,30,chunancha tamam firshton ne sajda kya
  15,31,siwaye iblees ke ke uss ne sajda karne walon ka sath dainay se inkaar kar diya
  15,32,"rab ne poocha"" ae iblees, tujhe kya howa ke to ne sajda karne walon ka sath nah diya ?"
  15,33,"is ne kaha"" mera yeh kaam nahi hai ke mein iss bashar ko sajda karoon jisay to ne sari hui matti ke sokhey gaaray se peda kya hai """
  15,34,"rab ne farmaya"" acha to nikal ja yahan se kyunkay to mardood hai"
  15,35,"aur ab roz jaza taq tujh par laanat hai """
  15,36,"uss ne arz kya"" mere rab, yeh baat hai to phir mujhe uss roz taq ke liye mohlat day jabkay sab ensaan dobarah uthaye jayen ge """
  15,37,"farmaya"" acha, tujhe mohlat hai"
  15,38,"uss din taq jis ka waqt hamein maloom hai """
  15,39,"woh bola"" mere rab, jaissa to ne mujhe behkaya usi terhan ab mein zameen mein inn ke liye dil فریبیاں peda kar ke inn sab ko b_hka dun ga"
  15,40,"siwaye tairay unn bundon ke jinhein to ne inn mein se khalis kar liya ho """
  15,41,"farmaya"" yeh rasta hai jo seedha mujh taq pohanchana hai"
  15,42,"be shak, jo mere haqeeqi bande hain un par tera bas nah chalay ga tera bas to sirf unn behke hue logon hi par chalay ga jo teri pairwi karen"
  15,43,"aur un sab ke liye jahannum ki vayd hai """
  15,44,yeh jahannum ( jis ki wa'id perwaneiblees ke liye ki gayi hai ) is ke saat darwazay hain har darwazay ke liye unn mein se aik hissa makhsoos kar diya gaya hai
  15,45,bakhilaf iss ke mut-taqi log baghoon aur chashmo mein hon ge
  15,46,aur unn se kaha jaye ga ke daakhil ho jao un mein salamti ke sath be khauf o khatar
  15,47,"unn ke dilon mein jo thori bohat khout kapat hogi usay hum nikaal den ge, woh aapas mein bhai bhai ban kar aamnay samnay takhton par bathain ge"
  15,48,unhen nah wahan kisi mushaqqat se paala parre ga aur nah woh wahan se nikalay jayen ge
  15,49,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, mere bundon ko khabar day do ke mein bohat dar guzar karne wala aur Raheem hon"
  15,50,magar iss ke sath mera azaab bhi nihayat dard naak azaab hai
  15,51,aur inhen zara ibrahim ke mehmanon ka qissa sunaaoo
  15,52,"jab woh aeye uss ke haan aur kaha"" salam ho tum par,"" to uss ne kaha"" hamein tum se dar lagta hai """
  15,53,"onhon ne jawab diya"" daro nahi, hum tumhe aik barray syane larke ki basharat dete hain """
  15,54,"ibrahim ne kaha"" kya tum iss burhapay mein mujhe aulaad ki basharat dete ho? zara socho to sahi ke yeh kaisi basharat tum mujhe day rahay ho? """
  15,55,"onhon ne jawab diya"" hum tumhe brhq basharat day rahay hain, tum mayoos nah ho """
  15,56,"ibrahim ne kaha"" apne rab ki rehmat se mayoos to gumraah log hi howa karte hain """
  15,57,"phir ibrahim ne poocha"" ae faristganeEllahi, woh muhim kya hai jis par aap hazraat tashreef laaye hain? """
  15,58,"woh bolay,"" hum aik mujrim qoum ki taraf beje gay hain"
  15,59,"sirf loot ke ghar walay mustasna hain, un sab ko hum bacha len ge"
  15,60,"siwaye uss ki biwi ke jis ke liye ( Allah farmata hai ke ) hum ne muqaddar kar diya hai ke woh peechay reh jaane walon mein shaamil rahay gi """
  15,61,phir jab yeh fristadayloot ke haan puhanche
  15,62,"to uss ne kaha"" aap log ajnabi maloom hotay hain """
  15,63,"onhon ne jawab diya"" nahi, balkay hum wohi cheez le kar aeye hain jis ke anay mein yeh log shak kar rahay thay"
  15,64,hum tum se sach kehte hain ke hum haq ke sath tumahray paas aeye hain
  15,65,"lehaza ab tum kuch raat rahay apne ghar walon ko le kar nikal jao aur khud un ke peechay peechay chalo tum mein se koi palat kar nah dekhe bas seedhay chalay jao jidhar jaane ka tumhe hukum diya ja raha hai """
  15,66,aur ussay hum ne apna yeh faisla pouncha diya ke subah hotay hotay inn logon ki jarr kaat di jaye gi
  15,67,itnay mein shehar ke log khusi ke maaray be taab ho kar loot ke ghar charh aeye
  15,68,"loot ne kaha"" bhayio, yeh mere mehman hain, meri fazihat nah karo"
  15,69,"Allah se daro, mujhe ruswa nah karo """
  15,70,"woh bolay"" kya hum baarha tumhe mana nahi kar chuke hain ke duniya bhar ke thekay daar nah bano? """
  15,71,"loot ne aajiz ho kar kaha"" agar tumhe kuch karna hi hai to yeh meri betiyan mojood hain! """
  15,72,"teri jaan ki qasam ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, uss waqt unn par aik nasha sa charha howa tha jis mein woh aapay se bahar hue jatay thay"
  15,73,aakhir kaar po phtte hi unn ko aik zabardast dhamakay ne aa liya
  15,74,aur hum ne uss bastii ko tall patt kar ke rakh diya aur un par paki hui matti ke patharon ki barish barsa di
  15,75,iss waqeye mein barri nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo sahib firasat hain
  15,76,aur woh ilaqa ( jahan yeh waqea paish aaya tha ) guzargah aam par waqay hai
  15,77,uss mein samaan Ibrat hai unn logon ke liye jo sahib imaan hain
  15,78,aur aikahwalay zalim thay
  15,79,"to dekh lau ke hum ne bhi unn se intiqam liya, aur inn dono qomon ke ujre hue ilaqay khulay rastay par waqay hain"
  15,80,hijr ke log bhi Rasolo-n ki tkzib kar chuke hain
  15,81,"hum ne apni ayaat unn ke paas bhejen, apni nishanain unn ko deikhein, magar woh sab ko nazar andaaz hi karte rahay"
  15,82,woh pahar taraash taraash kar makaan banatay thay aur apni jagah bilkul be khauf aur mutmaen thay
  15,83,aakhir kaar aik zabardast dhamakay ne unn ko subah hotay aa liya
  15,84,aur unn ki kamaai unn ke kuch kaam nah aayi
  15,85,"hum ne zameen aur aasman ko aur un ki sab mojoodaat ko haq ke siwa kisi aur bunyaad par Khalq nahi kya hai, aur faislay ki gharri yaqeenan anay wali hai, pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum ( inn logon kibehodgiyunpar ) sharefana dar guzar se kaam lau"
  15,86,yaqeenan tumhara rab sab ka khaaliq hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai
  15,87,"hum ne tum ko saat aisi ayatain day rakhi hain jo baar baar duhrai jaane ke Laiq hain, aur tumhe quran azeem ataa kya hai"
  15,88,"tum uss mata duniya ki taraf aankhh utha kar nah dekho jo hum ne inn mein se mukhtalif qisam ke logon ko day rakhi hai, aur nah inn ke haal par apna dil kurrhao inhen chore kar imaan laane walon ki taraf jhuko"
  15,89,aur ( nah maan-ne walon se ) keh do ke mein to saaf saaf tanbeeh karne wala hon
  15,90,yeh usi ki terhan ki tanbeeh hai jaisi hum ne unn tafarruqa prdazon ki taraf bhaije thi
  15,91,jinhon ne apne quran ko tukre tukre kar dala hai
  15,92,"tu qasam hai tairay Rab ki, hum zaroor un sab se poucheen ge"
  15,93,ke tum kya karte rahay ho
  15,94,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jis cheez ka tumhe hukum diya ja raha hai, ussay hankaypukare keh do aur shirk karne walon ki zara parwa nah karo"
  15,95,tumhari taraf se hum unn mazaq urane walon ki khabar lainay ke liye kaafi hain
  15,96,jo Allah ke sath kisi aur ko bhi khuda qarar dete hain anqareeb inhen maloom ho jaye ga
  15,97,hamein maloom hai ke jo baatein yeh log tum par banatay hain un se tumahray dil ko sakht kofat hoti hai
  15,98,"is ka ilaaj yeh hai ke apne rab ki hamd ke sath is ki tasbeeh karo, is ki janab mein sajda baja lao"
  15,99,aur uss aakhri gharri taq apne rab ki bandagi karte raho jis ka aana yakeeni hai
